document_data.mainbody:
'''House Jordain''' was an academy for the [[Jordain vizier]]s located on the southern coast of [[Halruaa]], looking over the [[Great Sea]]. This is where the viziers were educated, both in the world at large as well as in the political machinations of their home kingdom.

{{quote|''A jordain thinks first, and only then speaks."''|Jordaini proverb}}

Although the academy formally answered to the [[Netyarch]], in reality they were an independent institution that only answered to the [[Halruaan magehound|magehounds]].
